EXPLANATION
BY THE LEGISLATIVE COUNCIL
OF
A N A C T
RELATING TO COURTS AND CIVIL PROCEDURE -- PROCEDURE GENERALLY -- FEES
***
1 This act would increase the maximum fees payable to sheriffs, sergeants, and constables
2 for the service of writs, citations, or subpoenas, from $45.00 to $70.00.
3 This act would take effect upon passage.
